reviews.review_text: Nicely Done Thanx Andrew F.  You have done another fine job.  Great sound, pretty good show, in fact my favorite from this run.  I love the vocals on Desolation.  I don't believe I've heard another last verse sung this way.  I am playing Space thru Sugar Mags on my radio show this week.  Peace.
